title: Bobby Dated Someone Who Dated A Backstreet Boy + Jon Pardi Admits Luke Bryan Bought Him A Lemon
itunes:title: Bobby Dated Someone Who Dated A Backstreet Boy + Jon Pardi Admits Luke Bryan Bought Him A Lemon
description:
Bobby responds to a listener’s email about dating a girl who once dated Michael Phelps, and explains he once dated a girl that dated a Backstreet Boy. Jon Pardi stops by with his dad to talk about new music and a tour gift he got from Luke Bryan that needs a lot of work. Also, Producer Raymundo pitches his latest ‘shark tank’ idea.
